name: Custom Bocote Plugs - Face Grain
description:
Don't see anything in my current inventory that's your size, shape, etc? Well you can have it! Just give me a few criteria and I'll make em. When you order, provide the following

 - Flare - Single, or Double
 - Front - Flat, Concave, Convex, Spike
 - Back - Flat, Concave, Convex, Spike
 
If you're VEGAN, and would prefer to opt out of the beeswax in the finish please include this in your details.

Your size not listed? No problem. Message me and we'll get em made!

All custom plugs will be cut within 2 business days and mailed out. 

*All orders containing 10, or more, pairs of custom cut plugs will be mailed out within 7-10 business days.
